content:
@WG-prioritization/alerts issue #85155 has been requested for prioritization.

Procedure

  • Priority?
  • Regression?
  • Notify people/groups?
  • Needs I-nominated?
From the title I thought it was a diagnostic regression
But the error cannot be reproduced on stable or on beta with the given MCVE
newer comments seems to point out to recent PR merged, therefore I think not yet landed in beta. I've tried a bisection, will post my results
misleading diagnostics are confusing, so I'd say a P-high (unless this occurrence hit is a less common case, therefore P-medium).
(well, if it's only on nightly perhaps a P-medium, maybe we just want to be sure it doesn't slip elsewhere)
assignining p-high as it seems to impact some crates (albeit only on nightly, but still). Issue is being tracked in #73961
